        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the koftas are cooking, add your <strong>bulgur wheat </strong>to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
