    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into thin wedges</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
