    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>yoghurt</strong> with <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chopped cucumber</strong>, your <strong>mint sauce</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> chunky</strong> <strong>tzatziki</strong></p>",
