    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> to the cooked bulgur with the<strong> remaining roasted garlic paste</strong> and <strong>Mediterranean seasoning</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>garlicky bulgur</strong></p>",
