    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Greek-style beef koftas </strong>over the <strong>garlicky bulgur </strong>with the <strong>lettuce</strong>,<strong> tomato wedges </strong>and<strong> remaining chopped cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Top the salad with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Serve with a dollop of <strong>chunky tzatziki</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
